Package org.openehr.am.aom2.constraint_model

Interface CDefinedObject

All Superinterfaces:
ArchetypeConstraint, CObject
All Known Subinterfaces:
CArchetypeRoot, CComplexObject, CDate, CDateTime, CInteger, COrdered, CPrimitiveObject, CString, CTemporal, CTerminologyCode, CTime
public interface CDefinedObject extends CObject
Abstract parent type of `C_OBJECT` subtypes that are defined by value, i.e. whose definitions are actually in the archetype rather than being by reference.
